<para style="p">For the chief musician; set to the Gittith style. A psalm of the sons of Korah.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />How lovely is the place where you live,</para>

<para style="q1">Yahweh of hosts!</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />I long for the courts of Yahweh, my desire for it has made me exhausted.</para>

<para style="q1">My heart and all of my being call out to the living God.</para>
